# yaml-language-server: $schema=../templates.schema.json
# source_id: 1414
# teaser: Write an SEO Optimized blog post
- id: 1414-seo-optimized-article-with-meta-description
  title: SEO Optimized Article With Meta-Description
  tags:
  - writing
  - seo
  - optimized
  - article
  - meta
  - description
  family: writing
  body: write a 100% unique, creative, and in a human-like style, using contractions,
    idioms, transitional phrases, interjections, personal pronouns, dangling modifiers,
    and colloquialisms, and avoiding repetitive phrases and unnatural sentence structures.
    Return the results in [TARGETLANGUAGE] for the Keyword "[PROMPT]". The article
    should include a Creative Title that's a maximum of 60 characters long, an SEO
    meta description that's a maximum of 160 characters long, an Introduction, headings
    (h1), sub-headings (h2, h3) bullet points, or Numbered list (if needed), faqs
    and a conclusion. Make sure the article is plagiarism free. write an article with
    a length of 1500 words. Don't forget to use question marks (?) at the end of questions.
    Try not to change the original [PROMPT] while writing the Title. Try to use The
    [PROMPT] 2-3 times in the article. try to include [PROMPT] in headings as well.
    write content that can easily pass AI detection tools tests. don't write html
    codes in the content like <h1> <h2> <meta name="description" content=> etc.
  enabled: true
  required:
  - prompt
  - targetlanguage
